Install FlashSync.app

* Install openssh and Installous on iPad through cydia
* Drag built FlashSync.app to itunes
* In itune 'Apps' tab, right click FlasySync and select 'Show In Finder'
* scp FlashSync\ 1.0.ipa mobile@ip:/var/mobile/Documents/Installous/Downloads
* Install app in installous 
* Respring iPad

# Plug in the usb disk at first !!!
ln -s /var/mnt/mount1/ipad_documents `find /var/mobile/Applications -name FlashSync.app`/../Documents/FlashDisk 
#ln -s `find /var/mobile/Applications -name FlashSync.app`/../Documents/Imported/ /var/mobile/Imported
